----------------------------------
None


18. cterror - Likelihood profile error computation
--------------------------------------------------
None


19. cscripts
------------
The csspec script now handled correctly stacked data. Dependent on the
requested energy binning, it selects for each spectral energy bin the
relevant energy bins from the counts cube and performs a maximum likelihood
analysis.


